ry again';&#xA;      result.style.color = &quot;#D1345B&quot;;&#xA;     }&#xA;    });&#xA;   });&#xA;  &lt;/script&gt;&#xA; &lt;/body&gt;&#xA;&lt;/html&gt;\" /><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>&lt;button&gt;</code> seguido de <code>D</code> e finalmente <code>&lt;/button&gt;</code>.</p></body></html>"
